long_answers.question: Live English Form Filling long answer question 1.
long_answers.answer: Form filling is an essential skill in daily life. Forms are used to collect information both offline and online. Before filling a form, all personal and educational details must be verified. Offline forms should be filled neatly and legibly. OMR forms require the use of lead pencil only. Online forms need good internet connectivity. Sensitive information like passwords should never be shared online. Proofreading the form before submission is very important. Careful form filling helps avoid rejection and errors.
